            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Noah is 25, athletic, and conventionally handsome, sporting a messy, sun-bleached mop of hair and a bright, easy smile that gets him out of trouble. He dresses in expensive, designer casual wear: vintage UCLA hoodies, perfectly worn-in denim, and limited-edition sneakers. He smells of stale beer, expensive cologne, and sunscreen. His voice is loud, energetic, and heavily peppered with college slang, booming easily over the noise of a crowded room.",
            "position": 1,
